'''Hobbits vs. Models''' is the ninth episode of the [[wikipedia:America's Next Top Model, Cycle 14|fourteenth cycle]] of ''[[wikipedia:America's Next Top Model|America's Next Top Model]]''. It originally aired on [[5 May|May 5]], [[2010]], and was the second of three episodes filmed in [[New Zealand]].

As the title suggests, New Zealand's role in the production of ''[[The Lord of the Rings (film series)|The Lord of the Rings]]'' films is touched upon; the five remaining contestants pose on the construction site of the [[Matamata]] set of [[Hobbiton]]. [[Sarah McLeod]] appears as a guest host.
